body_html:
@cwhipkey re: selective registration docs.

@Lakedaemon If there are useful ops that you think should be included in the default set please feel free to send a PR adding them. It's our intention for the AAR to be useful for the majority of common models and a stepping stone before developers build their own size-optimized TF library.
